        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "在270-330°C的温度范围内，在Pd/β沸石催化剂上催化转化硬脂酸（模型化合物）。反应在15 bar氮气压力下的间歇反应器中进行，无外加氢气。产物包括C8-C11（裂解产物）和C12-C18（喷气燃料范围）的烃类。",
        "text_snippet": "The catalytic conversion of non-edible oil was carried out over a Pd-based zeolite catalyst in a single-step process (SSP) with no added hydrogen... The conversion of stearic acid, a model fatty acid compound, reached 100% and the proportion of hydrocarbons in the jet-fuel range was 69.3% over a Pd/beta-zeolite catalyst at 270°C in a SSP.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Cracking reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "催化裂解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "在300°C下，使用Pd/β沸石催化剂催化转化废豆油（SBO），反应6小时。目的是直接生产喷气燃料范围的烃类，并实现脱氧。",
        "text_snippet": "Through the catalytic conversion of raw materials, waste soybean oil (SBO)... a high-quality jet-fuel product was also obtained in a SSP. The degree of oxygen removal was approximately 95% for the conversions of SBO...",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Cracking reaction"
      },
      {
