        "description": "在300°C下，使用Pd/β沸石催化剂催化转化棕榈脂肪酸馏出物（PFAD），反应6小时。目的是直接生产喷气燃料范围的烃类，并实现脱氧。",
        "text_snippet": "Through the catalytic conversion of raw materials... palm fatty acid distillate (PFAD), a high-quality jet-fuel product was also obtained in a SSP. The degree of oxygen removal was approximately 95% for the conversions of... PFAD.",
